{"id":128357,"type":4,"name":"Army Men: World War","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d0/0b/128357_hwyHY.jpg","rating":{"total":8,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":2,"7":3,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.8},"summary":"《玩具兵大战：世界大战》，在国内又被称为《玩具兵大战5》，是一款以塑料玩具兵为主题的战略游戏。虽然对于当时大多数国内PC游戏玩家来说本作是他们接触到的第五部《玩具兵大战》系列的作品并被很多人称为“玩具兵大战 5”，但本作并非是《玩具兵大战》系列的第五作。\r\n\r\n本作采用的引擎和二代相比变化不大，画面也十分类似，有种一成不变的感觉。但是和《玩具兵大战2》基于小队而精细于队长Sarge的设计不同，完全设定在塑料玩具兵世界中的本作中不曾出现如Sarge或是Hawk Sarge那样的“英雄”人物，玩家在以二战战役（如诺曼底登陆、市场花园行动等）为蓝本设计的任务中需要控制部队完成一系列任务，因此游戏在操控上为控制数量较多的士兵进行了优化。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>玩具兵大战：世界大战</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/17864\">3DO</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Army Men: Operation Meltdown</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>玩具兵大战5</li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>RTT</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2000</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":11,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"PC","count":2},{"name":"童年","count":1},{"name":"欧美系","count":1},{"name":"RPG","count":1},{"name":"FPS","count":1},{"name":"ACT","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":17864,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/19/81/17864_prsn_E6wX5.jpg","name":"3DO","desc":"开发"}],"relations":[{"id":111907,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/19/57/111907_rQZ66.jpg","title":"Army Men","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/111907"},{"id":111908,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ef/65/111908_Q2nQ7.jpg","title":"Army Men 2","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/111908"},{"id":128266,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/08/81/128266_n9v9m.jpg","title":"Army Men: Toys in Space","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/128266"},{"id":128268,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/07/8f/128268_7w61b.jpg","title":"Army Men: Air Tactics","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/128268"},{"id":128369,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f1/85/128369_T6qos.jpg","title":"Army Men: RTS","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/128369"}]}